The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Kapil to conduct clinic in China

Beijing: Former India captain Kapil Dev will visit China this week to promote cricket in the most populous country of the world. 

Kapil will visit Chinas business hub Shanghai during the weekend. 

Kapil, also an amateur golfer, will have a golfing session in Shanghai on Friday. 

He will conduct Kapil Dev Kids Clinic on September 1 for children above the age of eight and will participate in a gala dinner. (PTI) 




